    ✅ **README updated:** Form A/B/C authoring examples with code snippets 
(lines 50-120).  
    ✅ **Inline comments:** JSDoc on builder method, promotion function, scanner
function.  
    ✅ **Arch-debt recorded:** Previous run identified follow-ups (regex 
robustness, watch resync test).
    
